
=== MapRegister === 
Send a MapRegister to the mapping service, wait for the MapNotify, and check it is correct.

=== MapRegister and MapRequest === 
Send a MapRegister to the mapping service, wait for the MapNotify , and check it is correct, 
and then send a MapRequest with the EID which was registered and wait for the MapReply, and check that we got The RLOC we registered.

=== MapRequest before MapRegister ===
Send a MapRequest, make sure that the MapReply has no RLOCs, send a MapRegister for that EID, 
send the MapRequest again and make sure that this time the MapReply contains the RLOC we registerd. 

